00141             int alpha,

00154 
00155             double alphaHalf = 0.5 * alpha;

00157 
00158             _alphabeta = (double)beta / (double)alpha;

00160             _pdfScaleLn =
00161                 alphaHalf * Math.Log(alpha)
00162                 + betaHalf * Math.Log(beta)
00163                 - Fn.BetaLn(alphaHalf, betaHalf);

00165             _pdfExponent2 = -alphaHalf - betaHalf;
